# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.1.0] - 2025-01-28

### Added

- Dynamic schema creation system for flexible content modeling
- JWT-based authentication with token renewal
- Role-based permission system (Admin, User Manager, Content Editor, Schema Editor)
- RESTful API for collections, entries, and schema management
- AWS S3 integration for file/image storage
- Email service integration (Brevo) for invitations and password reset
- Ollama AI integration for content generation
- Interactive Swagger/OpenAPI documentation
- Docker Compose setup for local MongoDB
- Comprehensive test suite with Jest and MongoDB Memory Server
- Winston logging with configurable levels
- Environment variable validation system
